formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1. The Certificate has been issued based on information and explanation given to us and books of account
and other records produced before us for verification by the management of company.
2. The project wise details of payments to vendor is not maintained in the books of accounts and we have relied
on the payments adjusted against project payables as certified by the management.
